mascara.title: Essence Mascara Lash Princess
mascara.description: The Essence Mascara Lash Princess is a popular mascara known for its volumizing and lengthening effects. Achieve dramatic lashes with this long-lasting and cruelty-free formula.

eyeshadow.title: Eyeshadow Palette with Mirror
eyeshadow.description: The Eyeshadow Palette with Mirror offers a versatile range of eyeshadow shades for creating stunning eye looks. With a built-in mirror, it's convenient for on-the-go makeup application.

face powder.title: Powder Canister
face powder.description: The Powder Canister is a finely milled setting powder designed to set makeup and control shine. With a lightweight and translucent formula, it provides a smooth and matte finish.

lipstick.title: Red Lipstick
lipstick.description: The Red Lipstick is a classic and bold choice for adding a pop of color to your lips. With a creamy and pigmented formula, it provides a vibrant and long-lasting finish.

nail polish.title: Red Nail Polish
nail polish.description: The Red Nail Polish offers a rich and glossy red hue for vibrant and polished nails. With a quick-drying formula, it provides a salon-quality finish at home.

perfumes.title: Calvin Klein CK One
perfumes.description: CK One by Calvin Klein is a classic unisex fragrance, known for its fresh and clean scent. It's a versatile fragrance suitable for everyday wear.

perfumes.title: Chanel Coco Noir Eau De
perfumes.description: Coco Noir by Chanel is an elegant and mysterious fragrance, featuring notes of grapefruit, rose, and sandalwood. Perfect for evening occasions.

perfumes.title: Dior J'adore
perfumes.description: J'adore by Dior is a luxurious and floral fragrance, known for its blend of ylang-ylang, rose, and jasmine. It embodies femininity and sophistication.

perfumes.title: Dolce Shine Eau de
perfumes.description: Dolce Shine by Dolce & Gabbana is a vibrant and fruity fragrance, featuring notes of mango, jasmine, and blonde woods. It's a joyful and youthful scent.

perfumes.title: Gucci Bloom Eau de
perfumes.description: Gucci Bloom by Gucci is a floral and captivating fragrance, with notes of tuberose, jasmine, and Rangoon creeper. It's a modern and romantic scent.

beds.title: Annibale Colombo Bed
beds.description: The Annibale Colombo Bed is a luxurious and elegant bed frame, crafted with high-quality materials for a comfortable and stylish bedroom.

sofas.title: Annibale Colombo Sofa
sofas.description: The Annibale Colombo Sofa is a sophisticated and comfortable seating option, featuring exquisite design and premium upholstery for your living room.

bedside tables.title: Bedside Table African Cherry
bedside tables.description: The Bedside Table in African Cherry is a stylish and functional addition to your bedroom, providing convenient storage space and a touch of elegance.

office chairs.title: Knoll Saarinen Executive Conference Chair
office chairs.description: The Knoll Saarinen Executive Conference Chair is a modern and ergonomic chair, perfect for your office or conference room with its timeless design.

bathroom.title: Wooden Bathroom Sink With Mirror
bathroom.description: The Wooden Bathroom Sink with Mirror is a unique and stylish addition to your bathroom, featuring a wooden sink countertop and a matching mirror.
